Package com.adobe.granite.timeline

Interface TimelineAggregator

  • public interface TimelineAggregator
    The TimelineAggregator is an OSGi-service providing creation of Timelines for the given resource. The service can be obtained from the OSGi service registry via the interface.

    • Method Summary

      • createTimeline

        Timeline createTimeline​(Resource resource)
        Create a Timeline for the given resource.

        Returns:

      • getTypes

        Map<String,​TimelineEventType> getTypes()
        Returns a collection of all known TimelineEventTypes. The types are provided by the TimelineEventProviders registered.
        Returns:
        A Map of TimelineEventTypes and their keys (names) - or an empty map if no providers are registered.
